data.description: Paradise Found in the Tiger Point Golf Course Community! This stunning home IS the Florida lifestyle. Spacious open feel as you enter this well maintained home. Large greatroom with wetbar, gas fireplace and French doors to the screened-in porch and pool. Beautiful kitchen with custom cabinetry, granite countertops with glass tiled backsplash, large breakfast bar and nook area, & updated high-end Stainless steel appliances featuring double wall oven & induction cooktop. The kitchen has tons of storage with 2 pantry areas and lots of cabinets. Just off the kitchen you will find the formal dining area with lots of sunlight and open to the greatroom. An office/study is conveniently located just off the foyer. Wonderful split floor plan with a private primary suite. The primary bedroom has 2 walk-in closets, fireplace, & French doors to the screened-in porch. The en-suite bath has dual vanity sinks, separate water closet, jetted tub, & separate shower. The additional bedrooms are adjoined by a jack-n-jill bathroom. Bedroom 3 has a large closet & door to the open covered back porch. Other highlights include Wood look LVP flooring throughout, soaring 14 ft ceilings, & inside laundry with pull down ironing board. Relax and enjoy the outdoor living on the screen porch by the inground pool with 2022 liner. The backyard also features a 6ft cedar privacy fence & open covered porch. There is room for RV & Boat storage behind the fence to stay within TPVHOA guidlines. Oversized, side entry garage that is temperature controlled by a mini split and a 220v plug, & circular driveway all on a .75 acre lot (one of the largest in Tiger Point)! Security system, smart HVAC system, in-ceiling surround sound speakers, 11/2020 roof, paid for Solar ($30/month power bill), Impact Windows, & tankless gas water heater make this home secure & efficient.  Schedule to see this beauty today!
